title: Nutanix Prism: Alerts
agents: nutanix
catalog: os/misc
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the alerts reported by a nutanix cluster.
 It will change status to {warn} and {crit} depending on the severity of
 the alert reported (this is controlled by the device itself).
 In addition, the latest message among those with the highest occuring severity
 will be displayed.
 Reported alerts can be acknowledged inside the Prism user interface.

 This check requires the special agent configurable through "Nutanix Prism".

inventory:
 One service is created.
